  (text "30000-40000 (4kW) - Option ROMs (all systems)\n40000-50000 (4kW) - Option ROMs (Non-Option 3 systems)\n"
    (at 38.735 139.7 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid 10e4bfab-8fa1-4f75-900d-db962a8d65ee)
  )
  (text "NOTE: a 64k EEPROM can be used, adding pin 1 to the bank selection (A15)"
    (at 95.885 167.005 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid 5cf0c63f-771d-414c-b5b9-375e649c545f)
  )
  (text "SW-1: Bank 0 (off for Bank 1)\n\nOther switches, on for \"enable\":\n\nSW-2: Adv. Prog.\nSW-3: Ext-IOa\nSW-4: Ext-IOb\nSW-5: Strings\nSW-6: Mass Storage\nSW-7: Gen. I/O\nSW-8: Plotter\nSW-9: Matrix ROM / Sys. Prog."
    (at 191.77 146.05 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid afba223e-6e76-49fd-ab72-311af5e6d4a1)
  )
  (text "NOTE: The IDA bus for the cartridges is - other then the \nentire rest of the system - NOT inverted! The buffer \ntranceivers HP used here are inverting! So both addresses \nand data bits come in and out right side up..."
    (at 96.52 179.705 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid b8a8fb98-91e5-4423-b274-f5f47af6b903)
  )

